information: The company GERHARDT WILLKOMM GARTEN- UND LANDSCHAFTSBAU GMBH, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1931, which operates in the Vegetables, edible roots and tubers industry. It also operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry, Nurseries, Textile plants, and Structural work industries. It is based in Uelzen, Germany.
